set_laundry_exit

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
set_laundry_exit -  Used to set the exit from the laundry entrance room into the laundry  itself.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void set_laundry_exit(string direc,
mixed dest,
string type)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^direction%^RESET%^ - The direction of the exit.
%^BOLD%^dest%^RESET%^ - The destination object. Usually the filename of the destination.
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - An exit type as in add_exit.
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
void.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/std/shops/laundry_entry_inherit.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Used to set the exit from the laundry entrance room into the laundry 
itself.
The parameters are just like those of add_exit.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
add_exit

.EP

